::Mosquitor/Striker::

Mosquitor screams in rage as shots hit his chest, his mechfluid flowing out. 
He turns to DarkMouse, aiming his acid gun and firing at her.

"DIE TRAITOR!!!" He yells shortly before a shot from Striker sends him flying 
through a tree.

Striker turns back to fire at Manterror as Mosquitor jumps back up, firing at 
DarkMouse.
